This is the final version of this map.  I will not be doing anything else with it as i've spent to much time on it and have other projects i want to get done.  

THis map is based on the film Assault on precinct 13.  I know it aint a faithfull recreation of the building but for the kind of gameplay i'm after it works.

Please enjoy the map as much as i enjoyed designing it.  You can play it on 212.187.247.11:27015.
